issue.title: ARM架构提效
issue.body: 请问，ARM架构apple主推mps，torch2.0版本以上已经支持了mps，但是modelscope目前看来是对torch的包装，但是这层包装没支持mps，可否支持mps，让M系列提升效率

pull_request.title: Support VLLM in LLMPipeline
pull_request.body:
test passed:
qwen/Qwen-7B-Chat
dtype=float16
sampling params:max_new_tokens=64, do_sample=True, top_p=1.0, top_k=20, temperature=1.0
Single thread testing, so no continous batching used, only paged attention

50 inferences.
without vllm: 5.56 per request, 16557MiB
with vllm:2.07 per request, 71659MiB

issue.title: mmcv问题
issue.body:
安装了mmcv-full1.7.0版本，但是在使用人脸检测时报错：
AssertionError: FacialLandmarkConfidencePipeline: FaceDetectionPipeline: DamoFdDetect: MMCV==1.7.0 is used but incompatible. Please install mmcv>=2.0.0rc4, <2.2.0.
这个是哪个库版本不匹配导致的？

issue.title: mmcv问题
issue.body:
安装了mmcv-full1.7.0版本，但是在使用人脸检测时报错：
AssertionError: FacialLandmarkConfidencePipeline: FaceDetectionPipeline: DamoFdDetect: MMCV==1.7.0 is used but incompatible. Please install mmcv>=2.0.0rc4, <2.2.0.
这个是哪个库版本不匹配导致的？

comment.body: 问题已解决，需要注意对应的mmdet与mmcv-full的版本关系，1.7.0对应的是2.26-2.28的mmdet版本

issue.title: StructBERT文本相似度模型无法下载
issue.body:
@liuyhwangyh 您好，我想下载`damo/nlp_structbert_sentence-similarity_chinese-base`，当下载到pytorch_model.bin文件的时候，报错404，但文件在页面的确存在的：https://modelscope.cn/models/damo/nlp_structbert_sentence-similarity_chinese-base/files

```python
from modelscope.pipelines import pipeline
from modelscope.utils.constant import Tasks

similarity_pipeline = pipeline(Tasks.sentence_similarity, 'damo/nlp_structbert_sentence-similarity_chinese-base')
similarity_pipeline(input=('商务职业学院和财经职业学院哪个好？', '商务职业学院商务管理在哪个校区？'))
```

错误信息：
```
   raise MaxRetryError(_pool, url, error or ResponseError(cause))
urllib3.exceptions.MaxRetryError: None: Max retries exceeded with url: http://www.modelscope.cn/api/v1/models/damo/nlp_structbert_sentence-similarity_chinese-base/repo?Revision=v1.0.1&FilePath=pytorch_model.bin (Caused by HTTPError('404 Client Error: Not Found for url: http://www.modelscope.cn/api/v1/models/damo/nlp_structbert_sentence-similarity_chinese-base/repo?Revision=v1.0.1&FilePath=pytorch_model.bin'))
```
